        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Extended Description</title>
            <para>Refer to
                <hotlnk xrefid="f082981125">Panel Light Outputs from EGC</hotlnk>.
            </para>
            <para>A variable voltage, controlled by the panel dimmer switch but generated in the EGC, is supplied at
                gauge cluster connector (1500) terminal 1 and circuit A62 through fuse F26. Voltage from the fuse is
                applied to circuit A62N to panel light adapter (1002). The panel light adapter is the source of panel
                light voltage for any other features with panel lights.
            </para>
        </svcsubproc>
